metadata.name: Shower Thought #1
metadata.description:
Hi, I'm Shower Thought #1.  
The first of her kind. 

Created by Haitian-American artist and graphic designer Sarah Duvivier. I'm a cyborg from a different dimension advocating for the destigmatization of mental health. You guessed it, even in my digital world, mental health matters. I try setting time out of my busy schedule to relax and hop in the matrix shower to unwind. Let's celebrate our small wins together.
